[{"id":"VR834502","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two systems, labeled System 1 and System 2, each containing two charged particles in a vertical line. In System 1, the top particle has charge positive Q, the bottom particle has charge positive 2 Q, and the distance between the two particles is D. In System 2, the top particle has charge positive 2 Q, the bottom particle has charge positive 2 Q, and the distance between the two particles is 2 D.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR834502.g02.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">The figure shows two systems, each with two charged particles. In System <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>, the particles have charges <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive Q\"><math alttext=\"positive Q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>+</mo><mi>Q</mi></mpadded></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 2 Q\"><math alttext=\"positive 2 Q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>Q</mi></mpadded></math></span></span> and are separated by a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"D\"><math alttext=\"D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>D</mi></math></span></span>. In System <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, each particle has charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 2 Q\"><math alttext=\"positive 2 Q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>Q</mi></math></span></span> and the particles are separated by a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 D\"><math alttext=\"2 D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mi>D</mi></math></span></span>. If the electric potential energy of System <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U sub 1\"><math alttext=\"U sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>, what is the electric potential energy of System <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> ?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR834502_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"one half U sub 1\"><math alttext=\"one half U sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U sub 1\"><math alttext=\"U sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 U sub 1\"><math alttext=\"2 U sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 U sub 1\"><math alttext=\"4 U sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":1}]